---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Consulting Services | Jennifer Chong — Board Governance Singapore"
  description="Board governance audits, SGX compliance reviews, female director recruitment, and full governance transformation. Three service tiers from $8,000 to $50,000."
>

<!-- ===== PAGE HERO ===== -->
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label" style="color:var(--gold-light);">What I Offer</span>
    <h1>Board Governance Consulting Services</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Comprehensive services to strengthen your board — from audit and assessment to female director recruitment and full transformation support.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== THREE TIERS OVERVIEW ===== -->
<section class="bg-gray">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header centered">
      <span class="section-label">Three Ways to Work With Me</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Choose Your Engagement Level</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
      <div class="card fade-up" style="border-top:4px solid var(--gray-400);">
        <div class="card-body" style="text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">🔍</div>
          <h3 style="color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.25rem;">Tier 1: Assessment</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.875rem; color:var(--gold); font-weight:700; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">$8,000 – $15,000 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 3–6 weeks</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem; margin:0;">Understand where you stand vs. compliance requirements and governance best practices.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card fade-up" style="border-top:4px solid var(--navy);">
        <div class="card-body" style="text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">🗺</div>
          <h3 style="color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.25rem;">Tier 2: Assessment + Strategy</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.875rem; color:var(--gold); font-weight:700; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">$18,000 – $25,000 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 8–12 weeks</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem; margin:0;">Full audit plus detailed improvement roadmap and female director recruitment strategy.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card fade-up" style="border-top:4px solid var(--gold);">
        <div class="card-body" style="text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">🚀</div>
          <h3 style="color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.25rem;">Tier 3: Full Transformation</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.875rem; color:var(--gold); font-weight:700; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">$35,000 – $50,000 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 12–18 months</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem; margin:0;">Assessment + strategy + hands-on implementation + ongoing advisory for 12+ months.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== TIER 1 ===== -->
<section class="bg-white" id="tier1">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="tier-header">
      <div class="tier-badge">1</div>
      <div>
        <h2>Tier 1 — Assessment Services</h2>
        <p class="tier-desc">Understand your current governance position. Ideal first step for any board.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-2">

      <div class="service-detail-card fade-up">
        <div class="sdc-header">
          <h3>Board Governance Audit</h3>
          <div class="sdc-pricing">
            <span class="sdc-price">$12,000 – $15,000</span>
            <span class="sdc-duration">4–6 weeks</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sdc-body">
          <p class="desc">Comprehensive assessment of your board's compliance with SGX requirements, governance best practices, and overall effectiveness.</p>
          <span class="sdc-section-label">Board Composition Analysis</span>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Current board size, independence, committee structure</li>
            <li>Skills assessment and diversity review</li>
            <li>Comparison to peer boards</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="sdc-section-label">SGX Compliance Review</span>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Director independence (Rule 710)</li>
            <li>Board composition (Rule 711)</li>
            <li>Audit committee (Rule 712)</li>
            <li>Remuneration disclosure (Rule 720)</li>
            <li>Gap identification and remediation plan</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="sdc-section-label">Deliverables</span>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Comprehensive audit report (25–40 pages)</li>
            <li>Board-level presentation</li>
            <li>Top 10 prioritised recommendations</li>
            <li>Compliance gap remediation plan</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="sdc-who-box" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
            <h5>Ideal For</h5>
            <ul class="check-list">
              <li>Boards wanting a governance health check</li>
              <li>Companies preparing for investor presentations</li>
              <li>Boards every 3–5 years (best practice)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-detail-card fade-up">
        <div class="sdc-header">
          <h3>Board Effectiveness Assessment</h3>
          <div class="sdc-pricing">
            <span class="sdc-price">$10,000 – $12,000</span>
            <span class="sdc-duration">4–5 weeks</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sdc-body">
          <p class="desc">Focused evaluation of how well your board actually functions — beyond compliance. Answers: Is your board making good decisions? Is there healthy debate?</p>
          <span class="sdc-section-label">Board Dynamics Assessment</span>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Survey of all board members</li>
            <li>Individual interviews (30–45 min each)</li>
            <li>Decision-making quality evaluation</li>
            <li>Trust and psychological safety assessment</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="sdc-section-label">Deliverables</span>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Board effectiveness score (1–10 scale)</li>
            <li>Benchmark comparison to peer boards</li>
            <li>Specific improvement recommendations</li>
            <li>Board evaluation framework design</li>
            <li>Action plan for board development</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="sdc-who-box" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
            <h5>Ideal For</h5>
            <ul class="check-list">
              <li>Boards wanting to improve effectiveness</li>
              <li>Organisations after governance challenges</li>
              <li>Boards undergoing significant changes</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-detail-card fade-up">
        <div class="sdc-header">
          <h3>SGX Compliance Review</h3>
          <div class="sdc-pricing">
            <span class="sdc-price">$8,000 – $10,000</span>
            <span class="sdc-duration">3–4 weeks</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sdc-body">
          <p class="desc">Focused assessment of compliance with SGX Listing Rules and Code of Corporate Governance — compliance verification without the full governance audit.</p>
          <span class="sdc-section-label">Key Rules Reviewed</span>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Rule 710: Director Independence</li>
            <li>Rule 711: Board Composition</li>
            <li>Rule 712: Audit Committee</li>
            <li>Rule 720: Remuneration Disclosure</li>
            <li>Rule 907: Related Party Transactions</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="sdc-section-label">Deliverables</span>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Point-by-point compliance assessment</li>
            <li>Remediation plan for each gap</li>
            <li>Compliance timeline and action checklist</li>
            <li>Board presentation</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="sdc-who-box" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
            <h5>Ideal For</h5>
            <ul class="check-list">
              <li>Companies with specific compliance concerns</li>
              <li>New board members needing orientation</li>
              <li>Boards preparing for regulator review</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-detail-card fade-up">
        <div class="sdc-header">
          <h3>Board Composition Review</h3>
          <div class="sdc-pricing">
            <span class="sdc-price">$8,000 – $10,000</span>
            <span class="sdc-duration">3–4 weeks</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sdc-body">
          <p class="desc">Assessment of whether your current board composition matches your organisation's needs and strategic direction — with a clear recruitment roadmap.</p>
          <span class="sdc-section-label">Assessment Includes</span>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Profile of each board member (expertise, tenure)</li>
            <li>Skills matrix — what expertise do you have?</li>
            <li>Expertise gaps — what's missing?</li>
            <li>Succession timeline (who's retiring when?)</li>
            <li>Future strategy alignment assessment</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="sdc-section-label">Deliverables</span>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Board composition assessment report</li>
            <li>Skills matrix visualisation</li>
            <li>3-year board composition roadmap</li>
            <li>Recruitment profile for new directors</li>
            <li>Succession planning recommendations</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="sdc-who-box" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
            <h5>Ideal For</h5>
            <ul class="check-list">
              <li>Boards with upcoming director retirements</li>
              <li>Companies preparing for digital transformation</li>
              <li>Boards making major strategic changes</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== TIER 2 ===== -->
<section class="bg-gray" id="tier2">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="tier-header">
      <div class="tier-badge" style="background:var(--gold);">2</div>
      <div>
        <h2>Tier 2 — Assessment + Strategy</h2>
        <p class="tier-desc">Audit + detailed roadmap + female director recruitment strategy. Most popular for boards ready to make real changes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="service-detail-card fade-up">
      <div class="sdc-header tier2">
        <div class="popular-badge">Most Popular</div>
        <h3>Board Governance Audit + Implementation Strategy</h3>
        <div class="sdc-pricing">
          <span class="sdc-price">$18,000 – $25,000</span>
          <span class="sdc-duration">8–12 weeks</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sdc-body">
        <p class="desc">Complete audit <em>plus</em> a detailed roadmap for improvement and a female director recruitment strategy — everything in Tier 1, plus a concrete plan to act on it.</p>
        <div class="sdc-cols">
          <div>
            <span class="sdc-section-label">3-Year Governance Roadmap</span>
            <ul class="check-list">
              <li>Prioritised actions (quick wins + long-term improvements)</li>
              <li>Timeline, milestones and responsibility assignment</li>
              <li>Success metrics and KPIs</li>
              <li>Progress tracking mechanism</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="sdc-section-label">Female Director Recruitment Strategy</span>
            <ul class="check-list">
              <li>Board diversity gap analysis</li>
              <li>10–15 qualified female director candidates identified</li>
              <li>Candidate assessment and ranking</li>
              <li>Interview preparation guide</li>
              <li>On-boarding programme design</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="sdc-section-label" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">Focused Strategy Areas (choose 2–3)</span>
        <div class="grid grid-3" style="gap:0.75rem; margin-top:0.5rem;">
          <span class="tag tag-navy">Risk Management Framework</span>
          <span class="tag tag-navy">Audit Committee Transformation</span>
          <span class="tag tag-navy">Succession Planning</span>
          <span class="tag tag-navy">Board Evaluation Programme</span>
          <span class="tag tag-navy">Remuneration Policy</span>
          <span class="tag tag-navy">ESG Governance</span>
        </div>
        <div class="sdc-who-box" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
          <h5>Ideal For</h5>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Boards serious about comprehensive improvement</li>
            <li>Organisations with significant governance gaps</li>
            <li>Companies wanting to strengthen diversity</li>
            <li>Boards committed to governance excellence</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== TIER 3 ===== -->
<section class="bg-white" id="tier3">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="tier-header">
      <div class="tier-badge" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),var(--gold-light));">3</div>
      <div>
        <h2>Tier 3 — Full Governance Transformation</h2>
        <p class="tier-desc">Complete audit + strategy + hands-on implementation + ongoing advisory for 12+ months.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="service-detail-card fade-up">
      <div class="sdc-header tier3">
        <h3>Full Governance Transformation + 12-Month Implementation Support</h3>
        <div class="sdc-pricing">
          <span class="sdc-price">$35,000 – $50,000</span>
          <span class="sdc-duration">12–18 months</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sdc-body">
        <p class="desc">Everything in Tier 2, plus hands-on implementation support, quarterly monitoring, ongoing advisory, and a true 12+ month partnership to embed sustainable governance excellence.</p>
        <div class="sdc-cols">
          <div>
            <span class="sdc-section-label">Implementation Support (Months 1–6)</span>
            <ul class="check-list">
              <li>Female director recruitment process coaching</li>
              <li>Board preparation for candidate interviews</li>
              <li>Interview facilitation and support</li>
              <li>New director on-boarding programme execution</li>
              <li>Director mentorship pairing</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="sdc-section-label">Ongoing Advisory (Months 6–18)</span>
            <ul class="check-list">
              <li>Monthly check-ins (first 3 months)</li>
              <li>Quarterly progress reviews</li>
              <li>KPI and milestone tracking</li>
              <li>Governance challenge consultation (ad-hoc)</li>
              <li>Continuous improvement support</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="sdc-section-label" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">Expected Outcomes</span>
        <div class="grid grid-2" style="gap:0.625rem; margin-top:0.5rem;">
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Female director(s) successfully appointed and integrated</li>
            <li>All major governance improvements implemented</li>
            <li>Board effectiveness significantly improved</li>
          </ul>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Sustainable governance practices embedded</li>
            <li>SGX compliance achieved and maintained</li>
            <li>Clear path to continued excellence</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== À LA CARTE ===== -->
<section class="bg-gray" id="addons">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-label">Add-On Services</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Specialist &amp; À La Carte Services</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Add to any tier, or engage independently for specific governance challenges.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-2">
      <div class="service-detail-card fade-up">
        <div class="sdc-header addon">
          <h3>Related Party Transaction Audit</h3>
          <div class="sdc-pricing">
            <span class="sdc-price">$5,000 – $8,000</span>
            <span class="sdc-duration">2–3 weeks</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sdc-body">
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Identify all related parties</li>
            <li>Assess proper disclosure and approval</li>
            <li>Arms-length nature assessment</li>
            <li>Risk assessment and remediation plan</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-detail-card fade-up">
        <div class="sdc-header addon">
          <h3>Board Succession Planning</h3>
          <div class="sdc-pricing">
            <span class="sdc-price">$10,000 – $15,000</span>
            <span class="sdc-duration">4–6 weeks</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sdc-body">
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Current situation assessment</li>
            <li>Potential internal successors identified</li>
            <li>Development plans for candidates</li>
            <li>External recruitment strategy</li>
            <li>Knowledge transfer plan</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-detail-card fade-up">
        <div class="sdc-header addon">
          <h3>Risk Management Framework Development</h3>
          <div class="sdc-pricing">
            <span class="sdc-price">$12,000 – $18,000</span>
            <span class="sdc-duration">6–8 weeks</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sdc-body">
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Risk management policy design</li>
            <li>Risk appetite statement</li>
            <li>Risk committee charter</li>
            <li>Risk assessment and reporting framework</li>
            <li>Staff training</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-detail-card fade-up">
        <div class="sdc-header addon">
          <h3>ESG &amp; Sustainability Governance</h3>
          <div class="sdc-pricing">
            <span class="sdc-price">$10,000 – $15,000</span>
            <span class="sdc-duration">4–6 weeks</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sdc-body">
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>ESG governance framework design</li>
            <li>Sustainability committee charter</li>
            <li>ESG reporting assessment</li>
            <li>SGX sustainability reporting alignment</li>
            <li>Stakeholder engagement strategy</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-detail-card fade-up">
        <div class="sdc-header addon">
          <h3>Executive Remuneration Review</h3>
          <div class="sdc-pricing">
            <span class="sdc-price">$8,000 – $10,000</span>
            <span class="sdc-duration">3–4 weeks</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sdc-body">
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Remuneration committee effectiveness</li>
            <li>Compensation structure analysis</li>
            <li>Peer benchmarking</li>
            <li>Disclosure assessment and policy recommendations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-detail-card fade-up">
        <div class="sdc-header addon">
          <h3>Ongoing Monthly Advisory</h3>
          <div class="sdc-pricing">
            <span class="sdc-price">$2,000 – $3,000/month</span>
            <span class="sdc-duration">No minimum commitment</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sdc-body">
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Monthly 1-hour governance advisory call</li>
            <li>Ad-hoc questions and issues support</li>
            <li>Ongoing guidance and recommendations</li>
            <li>No lock-in required</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

